"We slept and woke up to a fire alarm and people screaming.
We ran down the stairs and it took us about ten minutes to get down from the fiftieth floor," a skyscraper resident who identified himself as George told Reuters.
According to the Dubai Civil Defence Authority, fire brigades extinguished the fire at around 4:00 local time (00:00 GMT) and cooled the building.
